tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE unauthorized_changes (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  query VARCHAR(255),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE suspicious_activities (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  activity_type VARCHAR(50),
  description TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE sql_queries (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  query_text TEXT,
  user VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE table3 (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    table_name VARCHAR(50),
    change_type VARCHAR(50),
    change_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
